name: extreme_combo_deep_if_with_do_and_binding
section: feature-interactions-deep
args: cond:Bool setup:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Mixed helpers, direct dispatch, control flow, and bindings should compose without changing semantics.
law: (with [x (do {setup} (if {cond} (+ {a} {c}) (+ {b} {c})))] (= (- x {c}) (if {cond} {a} {b})))
